'''''Epilepsia''''' is a [[peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[medical journal]] focusing on all aspects of [[epilepsy]]. It is the official journal of the [[International League Against Epilepsy]], is published by [[Wiley-Blackwell]], and is edited by [[Philip A. Schwartzkroin]] and [[Simon D. Shorvon]].

